cast.overview: After their late former Captain is framed, Lowrey and Burnett try to clear his name, only to end up on the run themselves.
cast.title: Bad Boys: Ride or Die

details.biography: Nathan is an Atlanta born actor who has had a recent string of success in booking roles in upcoming shows like Florida Man and George and Tammy, and the upcoming movie Brothers. You may have seen him in the Oscar nominated Hillbilly Elegy last year as Bill, and this year in Vendetta. Along with film and TV Nathan has also appeared in several commercials such as Carmax and Checkers.
details.name: Nathan Hesse
